# Firmware Tests

This directory is reserved for PlatformIO unit and hardware-in-the-loop tests.

当前没有自动化固件测试。提交固件修改前至少执行：

```powershell
cd Firmware
pio run -j 1
```

Hardware changes should also be checked on an ESP32-C3 for serial commands, AP provisioning, UDP heartbeat timeout, the two-second connection animation, and exclusive red/green/yellow LED output.
